# ACR Automotive - Environment Variables Template
# Copy this file to create your local environment configuration

# =============================================================================
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
# =============================================================================
#
# For Local Development (using local Supabase):
#   1. Copy this file to .env.local
#   2. Use the local Supabase credentials (see below)
#   3. Run: npm run supabase:start
#   4. Run: npm run dev
#
# For Staging Environment:
#   1. Copy this file to .env.staging
#   2. Get staging credentials from team lead
#   3. Update all values with staging credentials
#
# For Production:
#   1. Copy this file to .env.production
#   2. Get production credentials from team lead (NEVER commit!)
#   3. Update all values with production credentials
#
# =============================================================================

